PKM Kriteria
API endpoints for managing PKM rubrik kriteria penilaian



GET
/pkm/{pkmId}/kriteria
Get list of kriteria for specific PKM


Returns all kriteria for a PKM with total bobot summary (Admin only)

Parameters
Try it out
Name	Description
pkmId *
integer
(path)
pkmId
Responses
Code	Description	Links
200	
Success

Media type

application/json
Controls Accept header.
Example Value
Schema
{
  "success": true,
  "data": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "pkm_id": 1,
      "urutan": 1,
      "judul": "Kreativitas dan Inovasi",
      "kriteria": "Mengukur tingkat kebaruan dan orisinalitas ide usaha yang diajukan...",
      "bobot": 30,
      "created_at": "2026-02-07T10:30:00+00:00",
      "updated_at": "2026-02-07T10:30:00+00:00"
    }
  ],
  "summary": {
    "total_kriteria": 4,
    "total_bobot": 100,
    "is_complete": true
  }
}
