POST
/pkm/{pkmId}/kriteria/reorder
Reorder kriteria


Update urutan of multiple kriteria at once (for drag & drop) (Admin only)

Parameters
Try it out
Name	Description
pkmId *
integer
(path)
pkmId
Request body

application/json
Example Value
Schema
{
  "orders": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "urutan": 1
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "urutan": 2
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "urutan": 3
    }
  ]
}